Option 1: Enter the container and run commands directly (easier)

powershell
# Enter the container
docker exec -it jms_core bash
Then inside the container, run these commands one by one:

bash
cd /opt/jumpserver/apps
python manage.py shell
Then at the Python shell (>>> prompt), type:

python
from settings.models import Setting
Setting.objects.update_or_create(
    name='LOGIN_CAPTCHA_ENABLED',
    defaults={'value': 'false', 'category': 'security'}
)
exit()
Then exit the container:

bash
exit
Then restart:

powershell
docker restart jms_core


